==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Rareripe
<hw>Rare"ripe`</hw> <pr>(-r⟦imac⟧p`)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Rare</ets> early + <ets>ripe</ets>. Cf.
<er>Rathripe</er>.]</ety> <def>Early ripe; ripe before others, or before
the usual season.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rareripe</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Rareripe
<hw>Rare"ripe`</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An early ripening fruit,
especially a kind of freestone peach.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Rarification</ent>⟦br⟧
